 <span data-ttu-id="bcf20-350">В следующем C# примере показано, как задать <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> для `true`свойства значение.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bcf20-350">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> property to `true`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
